            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row row-bordered no-gutters">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <a href="#">Liste over domfældelser</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 align-text-md-right mt-3 mt-md-0">
                <span class="badge badge-small badge-warning">I gang</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row row-bordered no-gutters">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <a href="#">Fremsæt finansielle beviser</a>
